_sText: This is my first map, I made it all myself with advice and ideas from Evil|Angus|UK and Vaatrad's tutorials, youTube 'vaatrad' to watch them, hint start with #1 and work your way up xD. The map is intended to be a short game, no longer than 2 minutes, and the other team isn't intended to cross the bridge.  They hide behind their brick walls and venture to their other areas. I haven't found any glitches so far but any recommendations are useful. There is work going on for an extra dimmension, the 'sewers' and basements etc. but i have other ideas and so it has been shunted to the back of the que.
